title: American Military Patch Guide - Detailed Color Guide
description:
The single most complete source on United States military patches. Color plates illustrate and identify more than 2,000 patches and tabs, from World War II to the present. Promises to become the definitive work on U.S. Army shoulder sleeve insignia and patches.
